text: Scutiger gongshanensis is a species of toad found in Gongshan County and Biluoxueshan 碧罗雪山 of Deqen County in Yunnan, China. Part of its range is within the Gaoligongshan National Nature Reserve. ==References== gongshanensis Category:Amphibians of China Category:Endemic fauna of Yunnan Category:Amphibians described in 1979
